3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses an ant colony system to apply the feature selection heuristics, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper uses sensitivity, specificity, and accuracy measurements to evaluate the performance of the recommended features subset, which are common evaluation metrics in information retrieval. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper uses an ant colony system, which is a type of evolutionary algorithm, to apply the feature selection heuristics.
